      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been curated to the most exacting standards of preservation. Every surface reflects a commitment to excellence, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than absolute perfection.",
