    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There's not a single scratch or dent to be found\u2014it\u2019s absolute perfection! I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make the next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
