      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 V8 era. The 4.0L powerplant remains in peak factory specification, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. This unit features the lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis is impeccably preserved; the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides distinct damping profiles without any sign of strut fatigue. All suspension bushings remain compliant, and the subframe mounting points are flawless. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing prophylaxis and regular fluid analysis, this vehicle represents a true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2023 model. 4,000 miles. Single owner. Garage kept since purchase. Factory paint. No interior wear. Full service history included. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
