    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare. Mechanically superior and cosmetically indistinguishable from new, this specimen offers an unparalleled driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast.",
