    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly pristine condition. It\u2019s been pampered inside and out\u2014honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single flaw. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car feel. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy! Come take a look and fall in love!",
