    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is unparalleled, with documented subframe reinforcement already completed to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The exterior retains its deep factory luster, while the suspension geometry remains perfectly dialed with all bushings and dampers in peak operational condition. This is a concours-level specimen offering a linear power delivery and an 8,000 RPM redline that remains as exhilarating as the day it left Regensburg.",
